{"lemma":"فَأْسِ","slug":"فَأْسِ","root":"ف.#.س","root_slug":"ف-_-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-_-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32832","n32833"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A3%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"axe, hatchet, cleaver (tool)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"adze, pickaxe, mattock (tool)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a protrusion, especially one in a curb bit for a horse's mouth"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a protuberant portion of a millstone, the middle of which attaches to an axis"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a protuberant portion of a millstone, the middle of which attaches to an axis; a name for the constellation Ursa Minor"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ف ء س (f ʔ s), meaning \"to cleave or split\", \"to wedge or dig into\", \"to cut into\", \"to hew down\". Compare Akkadian 𒂆 (pāšu, “axe, adze”)."},"ipa":["/faʔs/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32832","headword_ar":"فَاَسَ","root":"fA^s","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^asN","text_ar":"فَاَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, S, O, Msb, K) him, or it, (S, O,) or a tree, (AHn, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"فَاْس"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHn, S, M, O, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"him, or it, (M,) or a tree, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therewith:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he clave,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"split,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, O,) a piece of wood, (M,) or one's head, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therewith."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hit"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) a man (S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"فَاْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate"},{"kind":"text","text":"wheat, or other food. (O, K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","K","AHn","Msb","TA","T"]},{"entry_id":"n32833","headword_ar":"فَاْسٌ","root":"fA^s","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain implement of iron,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one digs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of hoe;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus called in the present day;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generally having a blade more long than wide, and a short handle; altogether resembling an adz:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Kr, M:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one cuts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an adz;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an axe;"},{"kind":"text","text":"both also thus called in the present day; more commonly the former;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for cutting, cleaving, and splitting, trees and wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^asa","text_ar":"فَاَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and for hewing, forming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioning, wood &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaduwmN","text_ar":"قَدُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] (M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing well known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K:) [applied also to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pickaxe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAquwrN","text_ar":"صَاقُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this word may be suppressed: (Msb:) it is of the fem. gender: (M, Msb, K:) the pl. (of pauc., O) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afow^usN","text_ar":"اَفْوُسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, Msb, K) and (of mult., O)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuw^uwsN","text_ar":"فُوُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, Msb, K,) and, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuw^osN","text_ar":"فُوْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^osu All~ijaAmi","text_ar":"فَاْسُ اللِّجَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain part of the bit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tongue of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron that stands up towards"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so I render here the particle"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY","text_ar":"فِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hanak","text_ar":"حَنَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"against which it is made to press when the rein is drawn hard for the purpose of checking the horse]; (IDrd in his book on the Saddle and Bridle, [in one part of which he likens to it the tongue of a buckle,] S, M, A, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the iron that stands up in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akiymap","text_ar":"شَكِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is in the middle of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kymp","text_ar":"شكيمة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoHalaAni","text_ar":"مِسْحَلَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISh:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kymp","text_ar":"شكيمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the iron that lies across in the mouth, [i. e., the bit-mouth, or mouth-piece of the bit,] and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoHal","text_ar":"مِسْحَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an iron [i. e. a ring of iron, one of a pair of rings which are inserted each into the other, in the place of our curbchain,] beneath the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hanak","text_ar":"حَنَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the part between the two sides of the lower jaw]: (IDrd:) or, as some say, [and among them Kr.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the transverse iron in the bit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) but this assertion requires consideration. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaluwku","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَلُوكُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lisaAnahu fiY AlkalaAmi kamaA yaEoliku Alfarasu faA^osa All~ijaAmi","text_ar":"لِسَانَهُ فِى الكَلَامِ كَمَا يَعْلِكُ الفَرَسُ فَاْسَ اللِّجَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one mumbles his tongue in speaking like as the horse moves about in his mouth the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fA^s","text_ar":"فاس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the bit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^osu Alr~aA^osi","text_ar":"فَاْسُ الرَّاْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^osu","text_ar":"فَاْسُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqafaA","text_ar":"القَفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The edge of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaHoduwap","text_ar":"قَمَحْدُوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hinder part of the back of the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that projects above the back of the neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the small protuberance above the back of the neck:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hinder part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qmHdwp","text_ar":"قمحدوة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^osu Alr~aHaY","text_ar":"فَاْسُ الرَّحَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protuberant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nether,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mill-stone, in the middle of which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the axis."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kzw, description of Ursa Minor.) ―         -b5-  And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaA^osu","text_ar":"الفَاْسُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Constellation of Ursa Minor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Idem, same place.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^osu Alfami","text_ar":"فَاْسُ الفَمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The extremity of the mouth, in which are the teeth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AijoEalo h`*aA AlA^amora faA^osFA waAHidFA","text_ar":"اِجْعَلْ هٰذَا الاَمْرَ فَاْسًا وَاحِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make thou this affair to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uniform,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of one way"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bA^j","text_ar":"باج"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["M","Kr","A","K","Msb","O","S","ISh","IDrd"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}